description: lint-before-output
globs: ["**/*.css","**/*.ts","**/*.tsx"]
---

When modifying CSS → run `pnpm lint:css:fix` then `pnpm lint:css`.
When modifying TS/TSX → run `pnpm lint:js:fix` then `pnpm lint:js`.

Do not proceed with final output if lint errors remain.
Fix errors in code only.
Never add ignore/disable comments.
List commands run.
